description:
SSH configuration parameters for each cell, including supported and selected MACs, key exchanges, and ciphers.
dateTime: Timestamp of the SSH configuration data.  Area_Name: Geographical area of the cell site. CellId: Unique identifier of the cell. Id2: Duplicate of CellId. Id3:  Redundant identifier (always '1'). Id4: Redundant identifier (always '1'). vsDataType: Data type identifier. vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format. Ssh.supportedMacs: Supported Message Authentication Codes. Ssh.supportedKeyExchanges: Supported key exchange algorithms. Ssh.selectedMacs: Selected MAC algorithm. Ssh.supportedCiphers: Supported encryption ciphers. Ssh.selectedCiphers: Selected encryption cipher. Ssh.sshId: SSH session identifier. Ssh.selectedKeyExchanges: Selected key exchange algorithm.
